text: I have an issue with the SEO recommendations tool flagging a bunch of `_hcms/analytics/search/conversion?` URLs that I’m not getting very far with support on. They’re deflecting the issue back at us and asking us where the page is hosted - obviously it’s HubSpot system page so very little I can do about it. Anyone had a similar issue?
Yes, I see this often, there isn't a fix that I've found other than hiding the notification to remove from future scans
